<p class="western" align="center">Combinação</p>
</td>
<td style="text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">
<p class="western" align="center"><img src="http://www.technovationchallenge.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/image04-1.png" alt="image04" width="135" height="112" /></p>
</td>
